	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Gallia</placeName> aliquot iam septimanas nihil certi habeo prater ea, quae in his continentur literis, et quod d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p629" cert="high">Coignetius</persName> ex aula scribit 27. iunii papistas vehementer tumultuari, sed nihilo minus longe et late propagari evangelium.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Uxorem et familiam <placeName ref="l491" cert="high">Argentorati</placeName> relictam revocavit in aulam; antea quoque d. <persName type="auto_name">Roya</persName> relicto <placeName ref="l491" cert="high">Argentorato</placeName> in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Galliam</placeName> rediit.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Metuunt viri prudentes turbas novas, quod nullus sit modus tyrannidis papistarum, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l378">Parisiensium</placeName> maxime.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vana sunt, quae referuntur de <persName type="citizen_name">Condensi</persName>, quasi papistarum sequatur religionem.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Verum tamen illud est, quod metu nimio multa impedit, neque ita neglectus et contemptus est in aula, sed inter primos.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non pudet quosdam hoc affirmare pro certo, quod ipsi factum optarent; erras tu forte in nomine; nam <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1097">Monasteriensem</placeName> episcopum invasit <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18716" cert="high">Erichus Brunsvicensis</persName>, non <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1030">Wirtzburgensem</placeName>, ut ex literis intelliges.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pugnaret cum canonibus et authoritate concilii, si alibi quam <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107" cert="high">Tridenti</placeName> concluderetur; <foreign xml:lang="de">ich acht aber wol, es stäcke darhinder, das man die execution wunderbarlich ordne, hebe und lege;</foreign> sed vicit agnus de tribu Iuda.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Iam nunc celebrantur comitia <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l21">Badae</placeName> inter <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l41">Bernenses</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2478">Sabaudiae</placeName> principis legatos, et legati, qui <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileae</placeName> fuerunt, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l21">Badam</placeName> redierunt.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid futurm sit, brevi audiemus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Der fürst wil vil;</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bern</placeName> wil wenig; werdent kum zamen kummen.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l646" cert="high">Claronensis</placeName> causa dilata est in 12. septembris resumenda <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l21">Badae</placeName> a sequestribus.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Man wart, wie es sich schicken wölle zuͦ <placeName type="auto_name">Haveldegras</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vivos voluerunt devorare Lutherani <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l61">Bremenses</placeName> quoque sed furere desierunt et salvi sunt <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l61">Bremenses</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="de" type="manual"><foreign xml:lang="la">Si <persName type="auto_name">Palatinus</persName> perseverarit</foreign>, werdend sy inn wol blyben lassen.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="de" type="manual"><foreign xml:lang="la">Haec causa gubernatur a deo; hic inclinat, quo vult</foreign>, und söltents all wild werden, der... elmaister <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p458">Brentz</persName> wirt ouch zuͦletst an das antthoupt kummen.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Gott läpt und ist gerächt.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Literas, quas hic tibi mitto fideliter, probe obsignatas remittes; uteris illis prudenter nec quibusvis communicabis.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quotidie ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Gallia</placeName> literas expecto.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quantum me attinet, aegroto iam tres septimanas; coepi hodie redire in sacram cathedram, verum confractis sim viribus et torpor totum occupavit corpus; caput debilitate opprimitur.</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed, quod visum est domino, cum hoc constet optimum esse, fiat.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non sine difficultate haec scribo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Wie kumpts, das ir so wenig hapt uß <placeName ref="l572" cert="high">Wirtenberg</placeName>? etc.</s>
					<s n="26" xml:lang="la" type="auto">30. iulii.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="27" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Saluta fratrem, sororem, nepotes etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="28" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus ille.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="29" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambrosio Blaurero</persName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l287" cert="high">Lüthmerkae</placeName> agenti, domino meo colendissimo et fratri charissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="30" xml:lang="de" type="auto">An m. <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambrosien Blaureren</persName> zuͦ <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l287" cert="high">Lüthmerken</placeName> im <placeName ref="l774" cert="high">Durgöw</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
